### Welcome to the RAML API portal for the <a href="https://calendar.google.com" target="_blank"><img src="data:image/png;base64," width="24px"> Google Calendar API</a>! 

This portal provides 
- a [RAML spec](/apiplatform/repository/public/organizations/30/apis/8157/versions/8356/files/root) describing the Google Calendar API in a clear, human- and machine-readable format
- [documentation](/apiplatform/popular/#/portals/apis/8157/versions/8356/pages/7064) of the Google Calendar API auto-generated from the RAML spec
- the [documentation](/apiplatform/popular/#/portals/apis/8157/versions/8356/pages/7064) is live: you can make calls to the Google Calendar API from the documentation
- live, documented usecases for the Google Calendar API, provided as API notebooks, and exercising much of the Google Calendar API

_This portal is built on the Anypoint Platform for APIs, using RAML version 0.8._

_For more information about RAML, see [http://raml.org](http://raml.org)._
